### Health (proxy via frontend)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Health (backend direct)
GET http://localhost:5002/api/health

### Auth login (backend)
POST http://localhost:5002/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@12345"
}

### Companies list (proxy)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/companies

### Companies create (backend)
POST http://localhost:5002/api/companies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smoke Co {{timestamp}}",
  "code": "SMK-{{timestamp}}",
  "type": "supplier",
  "email": "smoke{{timestamp}}@example.com",
  "phone": "+90-555-000-00-00"
}

### Companies import (backend)
POST http://localhost:5002/api/companies/import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companies": [
    { "name": "Import Smoke {{timestamp}}", "code": "IMPSMK-{{timestamp}}", "type": "Supplier", "email": "imp{{timestamp}}@example.com" },
    { "name": "Only-By-Name {{timestamp}}", "type": "Customer" }
  ]
}
